data.title: "Deo jinieoseu" ID Exchange (TV Episode 2015)
data.meta_description: ID Exchange: With Jang Dongmin, Oh Hyunmin, Hong Jin-ho, Lee Jun-Seok. This season of The Genius sees 13 former contestant battling it out in the Grand Final. The first game is a simple trading game - trade your card with others to gain points.
